                                                hardware capabilities, etc
                                            </li>
                                            <li>Actions – pages viewed, buttons clicked, time spent viewing, search
                                                keywords, etc
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="elementor-element elementor-element-a1271af elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading"
